high_descs: Walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and remove the cup.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave.
Place the cup in the microwave.
Approach the sink to your right.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Approach the microwave to your left.
Place the cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place two cups in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the fridge.
Take the gold glass out of the freezer.
Turn left and veer left to the microwave.
Place the glass in the microwave.
Take a step right.
Take the gold glass out of the sink.
Step left back to the microwave.
Place the glass in the microwave to the left of the other glass.
anns.task_desc: Place two glasses in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the fridge.
Get the gold glass out of the top of the fridge.
Turn to the left, walk to the microwave.
Place the gold glass in the microwave.
Take a step to the right, stand in front of the sink.
Pick up the gold glass in the sink.
Step in front of the microwave.
Place the gold glass in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place to gold glasses in the microwave.
